### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 🔐 AUTHENTIFICATION - OBTENIR LE TOKEN
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1️⃣ Obtenir Access & Refresh Tokens (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/token/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ♻️ RAFRAÎCHIR LE TOKEN
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 2️⃣ Rafraîchir quand ACCESS expire (optionnel)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/token/refresh/
# Content-Type: application/json
# 
# {
#   "refresh": "{{token}}"
# }


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 🏥 PATIENTS - OPÉRATIONS CRUD
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 3️⃣ Lister tous les patients
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 4️⃣ Créer un nouveau patient (FHIR format)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "resourceType": "Patient",
  "name": [
    {
      "family": "Martin",
      "given": ["Jean"]
    }
  ],
  "gender": "male",
  "birthDate": "1975-08-20"
}


### 5️⃣ Récupérer les détails d'un patient (remplacer l'ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 6️⃣ Modifier un patient
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "gender": "female"
}


### 7️⃣ Supprimer un patient
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 📊 OBSERVATIONS - CONSTANTES VITALES
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 8️⃣ Lister toutes les observations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/observations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 9️⃣ Créer une observation (glucose)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/observations/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "resourceType": "Observation",
  "code": {
    "coding": [
      {
        "system": "http://loinc.org",
        "code": "2345-7",
        "display": "Glucose"
      }
    ]
  },
  "subject": {
    "reference": "Patient/1"
  },
  "effectiveDateTime": "2024-03-04T10:30:00Z",
  "valueQuantity": {
    "value": 145,
    "unit": "mg/dL",
    "system": "http://unitsofmeasure.org"
  }
}


### 🔟 Créer une observation (tension artérielle)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/observations/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "resourceType": "Observation",
  "code": {
    "coding": [
      {
        "system": "http://loinc.org",
        "code": "85354-9",
        "display": "Blood Pressure"
      }
    ]
  },
  "subject": {
    "reference": "Patient/1"
  },
  "effectiveDateTime": "2024-03-04T10:30:00Z",
  "valueQuantity": {
    "value": 130,
    "unit": "mmHg"
  }
}


### 1️⃣1️⃣ Observations d'un patient spécifique
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/1/observations/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


